title: Musikbyran.Trashville.2008.Documentary-HELLsCUM
description:
It Features: 
    --Hank III, including live performances, commentary, 
    and a TOUR OF THE HAUNTED RANCH !!!

    --Joe Buck commentary and live performances.

    -- Joe Buck Giving a tour of downtown Nashville,
    including Music Row, The Country Music Hall of Fame's
    Williams' Family Exhibit, Tootsie's Orchid Lounge
    (where Outlaw Country was born), The Bluegrass Inn
    (where Shelton is at this very moment signing autographs.)

    --Creech Holler commentary
    
    --Jason from the underrated 'Jason and the Scorchers'
    singing to his pig. 

    --The Earnest Tubb Record Shop.

    --Excellent Cinemetography

    --And much much more. 

    You have GOT to see this. It's unbelievable there is
    nothing like this produced in the United States.
    It is from Sweden, and it is part of a series on 
    underground music all around the world.
